name: 37/∞ • 2020 daily experiment
description: experiment nº 37 from my series "•/∞" (2020), where I created images made with mobile apps. this one was made with mirrorlab's mirror tool and animated with movee's glitch video effect. original photography taken by vini cassol and edited on lightroom. taken: 2019, fundación proa, la boca, buenos aires - argentina, in front of dan flavin "Untitled (to Donna) 6, 1971".
